name: DAENIA CORGI
description:
The Daenia Glenumbran Corgi is a hardy working Dog from High Rock, renowned for its intelligence and natural herding abilities. It is one of two breeds known as Glenumbran Corgis, the other being the Cambray Glenumbran Corgi.

The Daenia Corgi has been a beloved companion of the Daggerfall royal family for over a century, beginning with Princess Imogneâ€™s first Dog, Gwendoline. All subsequent Royal Corgis are direct descendants of Gwendoline, and the breed has become an unofficial symbol of the Daggerfall monarchy.
